of the US Patent Office

00:01:34.066 --> 00:01:35.257
for the first time,

00:01:35.281 --> 00:01:38.956
and I sent my family a selfie
from that office in Virginia.

00:01:38.980 --> 00:01:39.981
(Laughter)

00:01:40.005 --> 00:01:41.900
